Fannie Mae
v.
Price 257P16-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 8, 2016 William Gerald Price, for Price, William Gerald. Natasha M. Barone, Attorney at Law, Fayetteville, for Federal National Mortgage Association a/k/a Fannie Mae.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st of September 2016 by Petitioner for Notice of Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of December 2016."
